<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>OTP Verification</title>
    <style>
        /* Global Styles */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h1 {
            color: #333;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .otp {
            color: #007bff;
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #f0f8ff;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        p {
            color: #555;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #aaa;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Hello, <%= name %></h1>
        <p>Your verification code is:</p>
        <div class="otp"><%= otp %></div>
        <p>Please use this OTP to complete your verification process. This code is valid for a limited time.</p>
        
        <p>If you didn't request this code, please ignore this email or contact support if you have any concerns.</p>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Thank you for using our service!</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
